Q: what does askr do?
A: Askr is an autonomous session orchestration tool for Claude Code that solves two problems: session exhaustion (when Claude hits context or quota limits mid-task) and team drift (when co-developers lose sync on project state). It monitors Claude sessions in real-time, checkpoints work before degradation occurs, resumes automatically, and keeps project state in git so both developers stay synchronized without manual explanation or standups.
